In my case, I managed to fix the issue by doing 2 things:

```
// svelte.config.js
const config = {
	kit: {
		...
		version: {
			pollInterval: 15_000 // In my case check for code updates every 15 seconds
		}
	}
}
```

and in my 'highest' layout:

```
// +layout.svelte
import { beforeNavigate } from '$app/navigation';

// Should fix white screen due to errors on try to import missing module by forcing a hard page reload if the version changed
beforeNavigate(({ to, willUnload }) => {
	if ($updated && willUnload && to?.url) {
		location.href = to.url.href;
	}
});
```
